Updated Golden Config jobs to route each device through its highest-weighted `GoldenConfigSetting` and honor that Setting's per-feature `enable_*` flag. Devices skipped because the winning Setting has the feature disabled log an `E3038` warning naming the Setting and weight; jobs with no eligible devices log a single `E3039` warning per feature. All in-scope Settings' repositories are still synced (so read-only consumers stay current), but only enabled Settings' repos are committed and pushed.
